  "title": "Route Zephyr fleet through RenodeServer",
  "description": "ec2-hetero-fleet.sh points SX1262.cs Renode nodes at generic SimulatorServer/NodeServer port 5555, which requires REGISTER first, while SX1262.cs sends TX first and is intentionally a no-REGISTER client. Start and assign per-node RenodeServer endpoints as scripts/renode-multinode.py does, preserving shared simulation traffic.",
